Name: Keanu Reeves
Bio: Keanu Reeves, in full Keanu Charles Reeves, Canadian actor who found his greatest success in comedy, science-fiction, and action movies. Reeves's mother was an English performer and costume designer, and his father was a Hawaiian geologist.

Name: Carrie-Anne Moss

Name: Benedict Cumberbatch
Bio: Benedict Timothy Carlton Cumberbatch was born and raised in London, England. His parents, Wanda Ventham and Timothy Carlton (born Timothy Carlton Congdon Cumberbatch), are both actors.

Name: Will Smith
Bio: Willard Carroll 'Will' Smith II is an American actor, comedian, producer, rapper, and songwriter.
